  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this randomised controlled trial is to test, whether telehealthcare can
      improve HRQOL and reduce emergency admissions and hospitalisations due to AECOPD. Different
      outcome parameters as described in the endpoints section will be analysed.
    </textblock>
